@startuml
participant ApiClient
participant AuthStore
participant API

ApiClient -> API : request with in-memory token
API --> ApiClient : 401
ApiClient -> AuthStore : single-flight refresh
AuthStore -> API : POST /auth/refresh\ncookie + CSRF
API --> AuthStore : new access token + user
AuthStore --> ApiClient : retry original request
ApiClient -> API : retried request
API --> ApiClient : success
@enduml
